          "text": "A 2-day-old infant dies of severe respiratory distress following a gestation complicated by persistent oligohydramnios. Upon examination at autopsy, the left kidney is noted to selectively lack cortical and medullary collecting ducts. From which of the following embryological structures do the cortical and medullary collecting ducts arise?",
